#: ../../../topics/settings.rst:204
msgid ""
"This setting also affects :setting:`DOWNLOAD_DELAY`: if :setting:"
"`CONCURRENT_REQUESTS_PER_IP` is non-zero, download delay is enforced per IP, "
"not per domain."
